{"about_the_game":"The Achtung Spitfire! campaign story is inspired by historical events, while its 20 missions have fictional circumstances and use randomization to increase replayability. In preparation for the Steam release, the campaign has been updated (all planes have tactical codes assigned, script bugs fixed, etc.).<br><br>Your character is a young Russian pilot from Siberia serving on the North Caucasus Front in late May 1943. The campaign features missions inspired by the Soviet 37th and 56th Armies attack on the German 44th Army Corps west of the city of Krymskaya. Your regiment will be flying the famous British-built Spitfire Mk.Vb which was loaned to the USSR via the Lend Lease program. Meeting Spitfires in the skies of the Kuban region came as quite a surprise to the Luftwaffe.<br><br>Experience fierce aerial combat in the skies above the picturesque Northern Caucasian region of the Soviet Union. Defend coastal ports on dawn patrols, escort friendly bombers over enemy territory and help suppress AAA batteries, but always be on the lookout for enemy fighters!<br><br><strong>Time frame:</strong> May 25th, 1943 - June 1st, 1943<br><strong>Regiment:</strong> 57th GIAP<br><strong>Available Aircraft:</strong> Spitfire Mk.Vb<br><strong>Duration:</strong> 20 missions<br><strong>Average total playtime:</strong> Approx. 12 hours<br><strong>Author:</strong> =The Syndicate=, updated by Jay =Jaegermeister= Yarbrough","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2731440/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734526020","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2731440/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1734526020","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2731440/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734526020","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2731440/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734526020","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id